data.description:
**RARE OPPORTUNITY, ASSUMABLE LOAN WITH 2.625% INTEREST RATE** Country living on a generous 1-Acre lot with NO HOA or CDD fees! Enjoy the serene and quiet surroundings while still being conveniently located to local areas of downtown St. Augustine. Currently operating as a successful Airbnb, this property is an ideal investment opportunity, or you can make it your forever home. The large shed outside provides ample storage for your toys and tools, making this property even more versatile. Currently operating as a successful Airbnb, this property is an ideal investment opportunity, or you can make it your forever home. This home has all the interior features of brick fireplace in spacious bright living room, Open kitchen with pantry cabinet and slow closing cabinets, Wine rack in the dining area, tiled bathrooms with bronze faucets & shower heads, Master has a walk-in closet, Brand new ceiling fans & light fixtures in every room, Laminate wood flooring in the bedrooms, NEW water softener ,Carbon tank & tannin filtration system in outdoor enclosed laundry room, New well pump installed in 2018, Side and and back door have between-the-glass blinds, Front yard security camera..The possibilities are endless with this huge lot, plenty of space for a pool and the fenced in yard gives you the security for storing your Boat & RV!

This well maintained home is 100% move in ready! Schedule your showing today.
